name: All Holiday Rentals
tag_list: vrbo, holiday-rentals, vacation-rentals, vacation-rentals-by-owner, holiday-accommodation, villa-rentals
overview:
All Holiday Rentals provides a sortable directory of all the major holiday rentals listing sites, including information on size, number of listings and geographic focus of each site. This information is useul to be holiday rental owners and those interested in renting holiday accommodation.

All Holiday Rentals also provides additional information for holiday rentals owners such asthe price of listings, free listing sites and special offers.

All Holiday Rentals also provides reviews of many of the more popular sites, including Homeaway, VRBO, Homelidays and Flipkey
